## How To Use

To run this project on your local machine:

1.  Clone the repository:
    ```sh
    git clone [https://github.com/prince-rai88/ClubPoster.git](https://github.com/prince-rai88/ClubPoster.git)
    ```
2.  Navigate into the project directory:
    ```sh
    cd ClubPoster
    ```
3.  Open the `poster.html` file in your web browser.